data.description: Come home to this conveniently located South Savannah property, affordably priced in the Villages at Villambrosa (Bradley Point South). This home has it all, new LVP flooring and paint throughout, a new roof, and beautiful quartz countertops in the kitchen and primary ensuite bath. Modern finishes are included in the secondary bath and downstairs powder room as well. Upstairs you'll find the generous primary suite, laundry room, and secondary bedrooms. You will love the front porch, rear entry garage access and the yard that is mowed by the HOA!
